Dave Sim hopes to cycle all 2077 miles of the 2015 Tour de France this summer . 
  The 36-year-old personal trainer from Southport is hoping to raise money for charity Help for Heroes . 
  He has spent months training to ride the Raleigh Chopper on the tour . 
  Mr Sim attempted the L'Etape du Tour last year and finished in the top 20 per cent of the race . 
 